String.string: Sorcha's challenge has begun.
Prepare for the first wave.
Prepare for the second wave.
Prepare for the third wave.
Sorcha is safe. You have won the challenge.
Help me! I'm being attacked!
The demons are getting through! Everyone, fall back!
Sorcha has less than half her HP. If Sorcha dies, the quest fails!
Keep it together! I've almost got it!
Somebody help! I can't fight them!
The demons are interfering! Get them off of me!
Quest failed. You will leave the instance in 3 seconds.
You are both suddenly paralyzed!
Both of you together? Good. Saves me some trouble.
Did you two think you could cheat a magister of the Iron Order and get away with it?
It was all this scoundrel's idea! You can let me go!
That's not going to happen. You're both dying today.
Wait! Wait! I'll give you your money back.
No need. I'll just take it off your corpse.
No! Please! Noooo!
I don't know whether you were really working with him or not. But you're a witness, so you can share the same grave.
Any last words?
Stop right there, Aknam!
Aknam, I'm placing you under arrest for conspiring to destroy the World Tree!
Conspiring? I destroyed the rotten hunk of wood myself!
And as for arresting me...guess again.
You leave us no choice!
Well...well struck...
Molva is behaving suspiciously. Follow Molva in secret.
So, this is the fabled World Tree sap?
I expected something more...exotic.
It is what it is. Now where's my money?
So impatient. But very well. Here's your reward.
Hold! You are all under arrest!
What the...?
Jovin? How did he find out...?
Jorivah? I thought Molva was meeting Zik!
Time for me to go, I think...!
Don't let him escape!
